import { Tab } from '@headlessui/react'
export const TabPriority = () => {
  return (
    <Tab.Group>
      <Tab.List>
        <Tab>Tab 1</Tab>
        <Tab>Tab 2</Tab>
        <Tab>Tab 3</Tab>
      </Tab.List>
      <Tab.Panels>
        <Tab.Panel>Content 1</Tab.Panel>
        <Tab.Panel>Content 2</Tab.Panel>
        <Tab.Panel>Content 3</Tab.Panel>
      </Tab.Panels>
    </Tab.Group>
  )
}
